definition: first case/first instance/first time (sth is done)
(prefix indicating ordinal number, e.g. first, number two etc)/order/(old) rank in the imperial examinations/mansion/(literary) but/just
one/1/single/a (article)/as soon as/entire/whole/all/throughout/"one" radical in Chinese characters (Kangxi radical 1)/also pr. [yao1] for greater clarity when spelling out numbers digit by digit

sentences.english: The first case is a 27 year old female from Jinan City, Shandong Province.
sentences.chinese: 第一例为一名来自山东省济南市的27岁妇女。

sentences.english: The first case is a 3 year-old female residing in Ninh Hoa District, Khanh Hoa Province.
sentences.chinese: 第一例是一名居住在庆和省宁和县的3岁女童。

sentences.english: The first newly confirmed case occurred in a 67-year-old woman from West Java Province.
sentences.chinese: 第一例新确认的病例发生于西爪哇省一名67岁妇女。

sentences.english: The first case is a 29 year old male from Vinh Phuc Province.
sentences.chinese: 第一例为来自永福省的一名29岁男子。

sentences.english: The first case occurred in a five-year-old male from East Bekasi, West Java Province.
sentences.chinese: 第一例发生于西爪哇省东勿加泗一名5岁男童。

sentences.english: First West Nile Virus-positive unit of blood intercepted.
sentences.chinese: 从血液中截获第一例西尼罗河病毒阳性单位。

sentences.english: Dr Nolen had butterflies in his stomach before he performed his first operation.
sentences.chinese: 诺兰医生在做第一例手术前感到很紧张。

sentences.english: The first newly detected case is a 10-year-old girl from the southern province of Long An.
sentences.chinese: 第一例最新发现的病例为南部隆安省一名10岁女孩。

sentences.english: The first newly reported case is a 35-year-old woman from the southern province of Dong Thap.
sentences.chinese: 第一例最新报告病例为南部同塔省的一名35岁妇女。

sentences.english: The first newly confirmed case was a 16-year-old girl from Jakarta.
sentences.chinese: 第一例新确认的病例为来自雅加达的一名16岁女孩。

sentences.english: The first retrospectively confirmed case was an 8-year-old female from Tangerang in Banten Province.
sentences.chinese: 第一例回顾性确诊病例为万丹省坦格朗一名8岁女童。

sentences.english: The first case is a 9-year-old boy from the southern province of Hunan.
sentences.chinese: 第一例为来自南部湖南省的一名9岁男童。
